author: CNET
description:
Don’t try this at home! ‼️💥

When CNET editor at large Andrew Lanxon heard some Cosmic Orange iPhones might be turning pink due to cleaning substances, he had to give it a try himself. After trying bleach and an oxy-active stain remover, his results were sadly unimpressive. 

Read about Andrew’s full experience: https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/i-tried-turning-my-cosmic-orange-iphone-17-pink-heres-what-happened/

#apple #iphone17 #fail #redditstories #experiment
title: Turning A Cosmic Orange iPhone 17 Pro… Pink?
